{"tid":477340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【長者血案】疑收音機噪音問題爭執　七旬翁遭生果刀刺胸亡","createTime":"2017-11-23T03:16:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T06:25:18.000Z","uid":8171,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"d24e6fcf2461a8bcd3a1f470b4326502cfb280e8","tid":477340,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T03:16:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/135695/thumbnail/6e5cc33f8c7cb7ac5d1f7db3c130edb7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F135695%2Fthumbnail%2F6e5cc33f8c7cb7ac5d1f7db3c130edb7.jpg&h=592b00fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沙田廣源邨發生兩老翁打鬥變兇殺案事件，77歲姓黎男子疑因於公園露天位置聽收音機聲浪太大，令一名73歲姓潘老翁不滿，兩人爭執下黎以生果刀刺向潘的胸口兩刀，傷者送院後證實傷重不治。警方於現場檢取一部收音機及一把生果刀，初步不排除兩人因收音機噪音問題爭執而釀成血案。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，死者潘X民人稱「貓叔」，一家4口住於廣榕樓，街坊指死者生前不時於街上飲酒，間中亦會與人口角，而他不時會行山，因此身上會攜帶刀，曾向街坊展示。據悉案發時疑犯黎X生懷疑於上址聽收音機時音量過大，引起死者不滿，兩人口角後發生打鬥，扭作一團，其後有人亮出生果刀，釀成血案。警方封鎖現場調查，檢走涉事的紅色收音機，以及一把4至5吋長、懷疑為兇器的生果刀。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/999459/xlarge/2c4676d3859a5a3160b7c8284ba3f3f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F999459%2Fxlarge%2F2c4676d3859a5a3160b7c8284ba3f3f3.jpg&h=02b11f12&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">現場近坑渠位置遺下大量血迹。　（蔡正邦攝）</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1000684/xlarge/c3f28bfb6986b01926a8bae6b9b2ffd0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1000684%2Fxlarge%2Fc3f28bfb6986b01926a8bae6b9b2ffd0.jpg&h=c1e98771&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">警員檢走懷疑兇刀。（林振華攝）</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1000691/xlarge/d9627444bbecd44414cf9e72af0d6e25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1000691%2Fxlarge%2Fd9627444bbecd44414cf9e72af0d6e25.jpg&h=f6fb0a3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/999376/xlarge/039fe5db5090f6f445b837f8cc3b92b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F999376%2Fxlarge%2F039fe5db5090f6f445b837f8cc3b92b1.jpg&h=41941915&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/999497/xlarge/55db7fa4f3e1496c1d0f64dd38597e22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F999497%2Fxlarge%2F55db7fa4f3e1496c1d0f64dd38597e22.jpg&h=e0fa07ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/999457/xlarge/4219136c8dac349c680a043b44440356.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F999457%2Fxlarge%2F4219136c8dac349c680a043b44440356.jpg&h=1c3154d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/999464/xlarge/198e3a36e6aaace4cea25e458bddf14a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F999464%2Fxlarge%2F198e3a36e6aaace4cea25e458bddf14a.jpg&h=349ebe52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n警方：不排除兩人不相識　因噪音問題爭執<br />\n<br />\n沙田警區助理指揮官（刑事）梁國榮表示，事發於下午3時12分，警方接報有人於廣源邨廣榕樓休憩公園發生打鬥，衝鋒隊到場發現兩名男子倒臥於地上，其中一人身有刀傷，兩人送院後，其中一名73歲姓潘男子於5時12分證實死亡，警方將另一名77歲姓黎男子拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1000680/xlarge/73bdcaf58f1237ef365d06d9a39312e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1000680%2Fxlarge%2F73bdcaf58f1237ef365d06d9a39312e1.jpg&h=746c5a10&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">77歲姓黎男子擦傷送院，其後被警拘捕。（黃偉民攝）</span><br />\n<br />\n梁國榮指死者胸口有兩處刀傷，疑犯則輕微擦傷，兩人無刑事紀錄，不排除兩人不相識，純粹因噪音問題發生口角，警方於現場檢取收音機、生果刀及啤酒罐，會調查涉案人有否飲酒。梁稱警方會繼續調查兩人關係，及由法醫驗屍確認死因，並呼籲目擊者與沙田重案組第1隊聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1000836/xlarge/75c15665de6a2a9c1e736c71afa1295b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1000836%2Fxlarge%2F75c15665de6a2a9c1e736c71afa1295b.jpg&h=b9bd8f8b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">仵工將死者遺體移送殮房。（林振華攝）</span>"},{"pid":"3e9383ad23587bf6e88ad90e93218c3e32615b63","tid":477340,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T03:40:17.000Z","msg":"真勇武<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8553555fd7bfe1d854a554041f4647eee53fdeb1","tid":477340,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T03:45:28.000Z","msg":"又係酒鬼又開大部機嘈鳩住哂，人地不滿又同人爭執<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n嘈音滋擾應該納入挑釁既其中一項囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c9c1a3decae0100b1a9cfcb307dcb2fed87ab52","tid":477340,"uid":8171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T06:25:18.000Z","msg":"噤鍾意大大聲聽收音機落去下面慢慢聽啦"}]}